Kau tak mau ikut menonton?

65
00:05:12,424 --> 00:05:13,717
Kau suka padaku?

66
00:05:15,301 --> 00:05:16,136
Apa?

67
00:05:20,515 --> 00:05:21,391
Benar.

68
00:05:22,934 --> 00:05:24,352
Aku benci padamu.

69
00:05:27,605 --> 00:05:28,690
Kenapa?

70
00:05:32,068 --> 00:05:33,695
