71
00:05:37,073 --> 00:05:38,074
Karena Pak Park.

72
00:05:40,577 --> 00:05:43,413
- Apa?
- Orang yang kau tabrak sampai mati.

73
00:05:45,623 --> 00:05:46,499
Pak Park.

74
00:05:50,462 --> 00:05:52,213
Dia seperti ayah bagiku.

75
