Kita jadi sering bertemu.

80
00:06:54,234 --> 00:06:55,401
Benar.

81
00:06:55,485 --> 00:06:57,237
<font color="#00ffff">PRESDIR JANG DAE-HEE</font>

82
00:06:57,320 --> 00:06:58,404
Mari kita lihat.

83
