126
00:09:52,120 --> 00:09:53,496
Bukankah sudah cukup?

127
00:09:56,958 --> 00:09:58,042
Park Saeroyi.

128
00:10:00,003 --> 00:10:02,255
Apa untungnya aku merusak hidupmu?

129
00:10:10,722 --> 00:10:12,140
Kau ingin aku melakukan apa?

130
