00:11:16,204 --> 00:11:17,330
musuhmu, Presdir Jang.

147
00:11:23,711 --> 00:11:26,464
Pada hari aku tak berlutut
dan dikeluarkan sekolah,

148
00:11:28,174 --> 00:11:32,720
