pada putranya.

149
00:11:34,847 --> 00:11:37,850
Dikeluarkan? Diusir?

150
00:11:39,811 --> 00:11:40,937
Kau...

151
00:11:42,146 --> 00:11:44,482
tak merebut apa pun dariku.

