160
00:12:21,227 --> 00:12:23,813
Mereka alasanku bisa terus berjualan.

161
00:12:26,023 --> 00:12:27,108
Baiklah.

162
00:12:32,029 --> 00:12:33,156
Haruskah kita coba?

163
