170
00:13:54,487 --> 00:13:55,488
Saeroyi.

171
00:14:00,243 --> 00:14:01,702
Kau di sini saat siang hari.

172
00:14:02,620 --> 00:14:04,497
Benar. Bagaimana denganmu?

